```

**Steps executed:**

1. `mkdir -p ~/m3pro_gazebo_ws/src && cd ~/m3pro_gazebo_ws/src`
2. `ros2 pkg create --build-type ament_cmake m3pro_gazebo --dependencies ros_gz_sim ros_gz_bridge gz_ros2_control xacro robot_state_publisher`
