| Check | Result |
|---|---|
| `colcon build` | ✅ 0.14 s |
| `xacro m3pro.xacro use_sim:=true` | ✅ 734 lines (580 base + 154 gated block) |
| `check_urdf` on sim expansion | ✅ `Successfully Parsed XML`, tree root unchanged |
| `xacro m3pro.xacro use_sim:=false` | ✅ 580 lines, Gazebo block stripped |
| `check_urdf` on real expansion | ✅ identical to post-S.3 state |
