**`tabletop.sdf` extras:**

- **Red cube `target_cube`**: 4 cm side, 20 g, placed at (0.25, 0, 0.02) — 25 cm directly in front of the robot's origin, resting on the ground plane. Inertia tensor computed as `(1/6) * m * L² = 5.33e-6 kg·m²` for all three diagonals. Friction µ = 1.0 on all contacts.
- **Blue open-top bin `drop_bin`**: 15×15 cm footprint, 10 cm tall, 5 mm wall thickness, static. Built as one floor + four walls (each its own collision/visual inside a single link). Placed at (0, 0.4, 0) — 40 cm to the robot's left. Open top so the arm can drop the cube in.
