**`spawn_robot.launch.py` pipeline:**

1. `xacro` substitution runs `xacro m3pro.xacro use_sim:=<arg>` and
   captures the stdout as a string.
2. `robot_state_publisher` publishes the result on
   `/robot_description` (transient-local QoS) and starts publishing
