  the plan), we will revisit.
- **No RViz config committed yet.** Saved configs become valuable
  after you know which displays you use. Committing one now would
  just be noise; added in a later polishing step if it proves
  worthwhile.
- **Verbose logging `-v 3` on Gazebo.** Useful for first-time debug;
  noisy but will catch the usual plugin-not-found / sensor-rendering
  errors on startup. Can be dialed back to `-v 2` once the sim is
